From the Infowars web site ::

On the Wednesday, April 18 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with U.S. Senator from Kentucky, Rand Paul, on a wide range subjects, including the TSA and the constitutional violations of the Obama administration. 

Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster newsletter also joins Alex to talk about the economy and other issues. 

Alex covers the news, including the extraordinary and growing power of the Goldman Sachs and the bankers and the most recent outrage by the TSA involving a 95 year old woman.
